<h1> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-hand-right"></span> Strategies:-</h1>
<div class="jumbotron">
<h2>Vision:</h2>
<p> Our vision is to uplift the standard and condition of life for orphans and vulnerable children and to empower young people to have a meaningfull life and a better tomorrow.The vision of G-sil guides us towards our goal of overcoming poverty and ensuring a life of dignity and security</p>
<h2>Mission:</h2>
<p> Our mission is to work with partners and volunteers to improve the lives of orphans.Vulnerable children and young people through a right-based approach.We focus on Children those who lost their parents to realize their rights,avail opportunities and build a better future for them.</p>
<h2>Aims and Objectives:</h2>
<p> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> The aim of the organization is to prevent chidren from roaming on the streets,to assist children who are orphaned due to HIV/AIDS, to achieve their goal of education and sustainable family life.</p><br/>
<p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> To uplift the quality of life of orphans and vulnerable children(ovc) by creating home enviornment.</p>
<p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> To empower ovc's of school going age by providing nutrition and educational and skill training.</p>
 <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> To protect and promote the well-being of ovc's rights and that of caregivers are protected,respected and fulfilled.</p>
